name: The Streets Wont Remember Me - old

metadata.name: Let's Talk Business
metadata.description:
As I was walking down the streets, I noticed what looked like a business meeting happening inside an electronics store. I stood there, wondering whether I should get the shoot, or just let them be.

Guess we know the answer now.
